NOTE ON GAME ASSETS
-------------------
This repository contains only original C++ source code. It does NOT include
any assets from "The Adventures of Captain Comic" (1988/1990).

All original game assets — graphics, sounds, level data, tile maps, and
related content — are Copyright 1990 by Michael A. Denio. They are not
covered by this license and are not distributed with this project.

To play the game, users must supply original game files obtained from a
legitimate source (e.g., the shareware release available at archive.org) and
run the extraction tools provided in the tools/ directory. See README.md for
instructions.
